<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog-Benachrichtigung</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .blog-post {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #007BFF;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .blog-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .blog-excerpt {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .read-more {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Neue Blog-Benachrichtigung</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hallo <%= recipientName %>,</p>
            <p>Es gibt einen neuen Blog-Beitrag, den du lesen solltest:</p>
            
            <div class="blog-post">
                <p class="blog-title"><%= blogPost.title %></p>
                <p class="blog-excerpt"><%= blogPost.excerpt %></p>
                <a href="<%= blogPost.url %>" class="read-more">Weiterlesen</a>
            </div>

            <p>Besuche unseren Blog, um weitere spannende Beitr√§ge zu entdecken.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Dein Unternehmen. Alle Rechte vorbehalten.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>